      {% comment %} FAQ Section {% endcomment %}
      <section class="contact-faq-section page-section section-alt-3">
        <div class="section-header">
          <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
          <p class="section-subtitle">
            Quick answers to common questions. Can't find what you're looking for? 
            Contact us using the forms above.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="faq-grid">
          <div class="faq-item">
            <h4>How quickly will I receive course access?</h4>
            <p>
              Course access is typically provided within 1-2 hours of purchase confirmation. 
              You'll receive an email with your unique access link and login instructions.
            </p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="faq-item">
            <h4>Are your certifications industry recognized?</h4>
            <p>
              Yes, AAI certifications are recognized by IAAPA and comply with ASTM F24 standards. 
              Our programs are accepted by leading amusement operators nationwide.
            </p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="faq-item">
            <h4>Can I access courses on mobile devices?</h4>
            <p>
              Absolutely! Our learning platform is fully optimized for mobile devices, 
              tablets, and desktops for learning anywhere, anytime.
            </p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="faq-item">
            <h4>Do you offer group discounts?</h4>
            <p>
              Yes, we offer volume discounts for organizations enrolling multiple employees. 
              Contact our corporate training team for customized pricing.
            </p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="faq-item">
            <h4>How long do I have to complete a course?</h4>
            <p>
              Course access is typically valid for 12 months from purchase date, giving you 
              flexibility to learn at your own pace and revisit materials as needed.
            </p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="faq-item">
            <h4>Are continuing education credits available?</h4>
            <p>
              Many of our courses offer CEU credits for professional development and 
              certification maintenance. Credit hours are clearly listed for each course.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

